# Cluster Map Status V4.4.17

## Release Title

Cluster Map Status V4.4.17

## Tag

v4.4.17

## Release Asset

Upload this ZIP to the release:

```text
Cluster_Map_Status_V4_4_17_EXE_Package.zip
```

## What Changed

- Added Project Evolution statement to About > Progress Summary.
- Added timeline image support for the where-it-started to where-it-is-now visual.
- Progress Summary now explains:
  - Where the app started
  - Where the app is now
  - Version timeline
  - Current project status

## Also Included

- Persistent data folder:
  - `Documents\Cluster Map Status Data`
- Desktop shortcut path fix.
- Dashboard restore.
- Update checker numeric version fix.
- GitHub update checker support.
